name: A letter to the lost souls of the world V2

metadata.name: I Spent This Year As a Ghost
metadata.description:
I miss the days where I would wake up full with energy
And would be excited to start my day.
I miss the days when I would find joy in the smallest of things.
I miss when I didn’t have to worry about my future
life didn’t matter at the time, I was free, alive, and happy
I miss that. 
Why can’t I feel that again? Man I would do anything to feel alive again. We live in a world with 7 billion people, but yet we feel so alone. 
Thing is I know people go through the things I’m going through, but it’s not the same. That doesn’t give me hope bc I feel like I’m battling through this alone.
Sometimes wish I'd stayed inside my mother
Never to come out.
